    Contains the data returned by Amazon S3 from the AmazonS3.upload(PresignedUrlUploadRequest) operation.

    Use this class to access metadata about the new object created from the AmazonS3.upload(PresignedUrlUploadRequest) operation. This class also contains the MD5 hash of the object content calculated on the client-side.
